'''诗巫圣伊丽沙白中学'''（{{lang-en|Saint Elizabeth Secondary School}}）是[[马来西亚|马来西亚]][[砂拉越州|砂拉越州]][[诗巫|诗巫]]的教会学校，于1902年由该市天主教会建立，坐落于美申路与南兰路交接处，原为女校，以[[英文|英文]]授课。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seehua.com/node/2609|title=反风越吹越炽，发展牌难满足城市选民|publisher=诗华资讯网}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.alumni.net/Asia/Malaysia/Sarawak/Sibu/Saint_Elizabeth%27s_Secondary_School/ |title=Saint Elizabeth Secondary School |publisher=Alumni.net |accessdate=2011-07-30 |archive-date=2011-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110412055716/http://www.alumni.net/Asia/Malaysia/Sarawak/Sibu/Saint_Elizabeth's_Secondary_School/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

